# 🛡️ Telemetry Ingestion & Trust Flow | PoWV Protocol

The **PoWV (Proof of Weighted Value) Protocol** transforms raw, trusted industrial telemetry into independently verifiable digital evidence through a hardware-assisted, layered trust architecture.

---

