Logical Processing Flow
The sequence below illustrates the end-to-end data lifecycle from acquisition to immutable proof registration:

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    
    participant D as 📟 Edge Device
    participant G as 🛡️ Secure Gateway
    participant V as 🔍 Verification Layer
    participant R as ⛓️ Evidence Registry

    D->>G: Submit trusted telemetry (Raw Payload)
    activate G
